django-pgrls
============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/packaging-poetry-purple.svg
      :alt: Packaging: Poetry
      :target: https://python-poetry.org/

.. image:: https://github.com/lorinkoz/django-pgrls/workflows/code/badge.svg
